SPELL NAME  : Cure Critical Wounds | Ranged Cure Critical wounds
SPELL SYNTAX: Ccw <target>         | RCcw <target>
SPELL COST  : 40 SP                | 80 SP
DESCRIPTION : Through the love of Mitra and the strength of the Cleric's faith,
	      the Cleric has the ability to provide massive healing for those
	      who have met with disaster. Invoking this aspect of Mitra's love
	      provides healing dependent upon both the faith and devotion
	      of the cleric. Though Mitra's love is strong, healing at a
	      distance will prove more taxing and its success dependent upon
	      the Cleric's devotion.
